VirtualBLS.net - Core Therapy Game Files

This repository contains the custom game logic and WordPress integration files for virtualBLS.net, a web-based video game adaptation of EMDR (Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing) therapy designed for use by trauma therapists.

